Introduction:

This document covers the basics of the GuardDog API, the exposed requests and authentication methods. 
	
Methods:
	Methods are sent as encoded json arrays. 

	Current:
	status - Returns a json encoded list of the current most state of each zone in the system. 
	getallresults - Returns a json encoded list of all the entires in the database. 
		I'll likely change this method in some way to provide a more secure experience.
	
	TODO:
	zonestate - Returns a json encoded list of the current state for the zone specified.
		inputs - zone.
	zonehistroy - Returns a json encoded list of the history for the specifed zone.
		inputs - zone.
	predictedevent = Returns the next predected event to occur on the system.

	

	
